Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Doctors' strike
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8hnj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 8 Jun 1975
Doctors strike over rocketing insurance cover. Growing malpractice suits blamed. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.